name: 23S rRNA (guanine745-N1)-methyltransferase
reaction: S-adenosyl-L-methionine + guanine745 in 23S rRNA = S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + N1-methylguanine745 in 23S rRNA [RN:R07233]
comment: The enzyme specifically methylates guanine745 at N1 in 23S rRNA.
